{"tid":1674862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post]想同大家傾下10月31日 附送日程表","createTime":"2019-10-25T12:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T04:51:07.000Z","uid":247940,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a1502dd8aef41563c643f95594e6adc9d33fe5f2","tid":1674862,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:53:20.000Z","msg":"10月21日黨鐵<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩點</span></span></strong>就封左元朗站<br />\n當時好亂 即日吹雞所有黨鐵站都可以悼念<br />\n但始終每條線可能2-3個站集合 大家好似冇咁散 <br />\n以下係我既提意 有錯請吊 因為對其他區都唔太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西鐵線：屯門 元朗<br />\n荃灣線：荃灣 太子 尖沙咀<br />\n東涌線：東涌 青衣<br />\n港島線：灣仔 北角 柴灣<br />\n火車線：沙田 粉嶺 九龍塘<br />\n馬鞍山線：馬鞍山<br />\n觀塘線：調景嶺 黃大仙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>希望可以有共識方便文宣方便大家到時聚人頭</strong></span></span><br />\n日後1121 1131⋯都可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨鐵喜歡的話封埋我以上講既站囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日程表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3EkpK6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3EkpK6.jpg&h=52b6bf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月26日 遮打見 18:00<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akN2C5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakN2C5m.jpg&h=5ec7a51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月27日 尖嘴見 15:00<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQ292xe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQ292xe.jpg&h=d7277b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月31日 毋望831 19:00<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQH6ki1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQH6ki1.jpg&h=c3c6dcd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁多先 唔該<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">準時</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\